articles ($\\chi = 5$), we observe an\nentirely different \"helical\" rise with completely unique features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jul 2020 08:01:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 Dec 2020 16:44:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-07"}
