 assessing the severity of\nfuture events. Our model may result in non-decaying discount factors (negative\ndiscount rates) for certain scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jul 2020 15:57:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 09:21:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 10:21:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
